# fn_tag dnIniSettingAllowSpacesInNames purpose Getter/setter for the 'allow_spaces_in_names' setting
# fn_tag dnIniSettingAllowSpacesInNames prints NIL
# fn_tag dnIniSettingAllowSpacesInNames returns Getter: boolean setting value, Setter: NIL
